__NAME__ purpose
specify directories containing code declaration blocks
__END__


__NAME__ synopsis
<arg choice='plain' rep='repeat'><replaceable>directory_name</replaceable></arg>
__END__


__NAME__ description
Specify directories containing tag, filter, widget, actionmap and other
code declarations.
__END__

__NAME__ notes
For more information on possible code declarations, see
&glos-ITL; and &glos-filter; glossary entries and the &conf-CodeDef;
configuration directive.
__END__


__NAME__ example: Setting __FILENAME__
<programlisting>
__FILENAME__ code etc/other_code
</programlisting>
__END__

